videos.headline: Not exactly how it's drawn up, but Colorado takes the lead recovering own fumble
videos.description: Colorado quarterback Sefo Liufau reaches for the goal line but gets hit and fumbles, but his teammates have his back as Alex Kelley dives on the ball in the end zone to put the Buffaloes ahead 7-0 on Colorado State.

videos.headline: Colorado keeps flying mile high with strip-sack recovery
videos.description: Already up 21-0 in the first quarter, Colorado keeps the pressure on when Jimmie Gilbert sacks Nick Stevens, causing a fumble that is recovered by Kenneth Olugbode and has the Buffaloes in position to score again.
